---
import '../../styles/site.css';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy - Daily</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/Blackhole.png">
</head>
<body class="plain-page-body">
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="site-header-leading">
      <a href="/" class="brand brand--static" aria-label="Jordan Moreno">Jordan Moreno</a>
    </div>
    <div class="site-header-trailing">
      <a href="/daily" class="header-link">Daily</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="header-link">Blog</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="privacy-page">
    <div class="privacy-content">
      <h1>Privacy Policy for Daily</h1>
      <p class="privacy-updated"><em>Last updated: March 27, 2026</em></p>

      <p>Daily is a personal journaling app. Your privacy is important to us.</p>

      <h2>Data Collection</h2>
      <p>Daily does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data to external servers. All journal entries, photos, and attachments are stored locally on your device.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>Daily does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.</p>

      <h2>Biometric Data</h2>
      <p>Daily offers an optional Face ID lock feature. Biometric authentication is handled entirely by your device's operating system. Daily does not access, store, or process any biometric data.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, you can reach me at <a href="mailto:jordan@accentuateai.app">jordan@accentuateai.app</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer plain-page-footer">
    <span class="footer-copy">&copy; <span id="year"></span></span>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear().toString();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
